flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Customer initiates onboarding process or reports a connectivity issue.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect customer onboarding data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: RCA Service - Analyze diagnostic logs]
  N2 --> N3{Agent: Agentic AI - Recommend remediation actions}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute remediation plan]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Process Builder - Escalate critical issues]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Notification - Notify customers about service interruptions]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Improved customer satisfaction, reduced downtime, increased activation revenue, and decreased churn.]
  N3 -->|High severity issue detected| B1[Auto-escalate to engineering team]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Immediate resolution]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|No actionable insights from diagnostics| B2[Request human intervention]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Manual troubleshooting]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Customer prefers self-service| B3[Provide detailed troubleshooting guide]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Empower customer self-resolution]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]